\f0\b\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Executive Summary\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa180\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The NIS2 Directive represents the European Union's most comprehensive cybersecurity regulation to date, directly impacting organizations providing essential and important services across all member states. Unlike voluntary frameworks, NIS2 establishes mandatory minimum security requirements with significant enforcement mechanisms.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb240\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs26 \cf3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Key Points for Board Consideration\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 Regulatory mandate: 
\f1\b0 NIS2 is law, not a voluntary standard. Compliance is required for in-scope entities.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	2.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 Enforcement timeline: 
\f1\b0 Belgium implemented October 2024; Netherlands expected Q2 2026. Enforcement is imminent.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	3.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 Board accountability: 
\f1\b0 Management bodies are explicitly accountable for oversight and approval of cybersecurity measures.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	4.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 Significant penalties: 
\f1\b0 Up to \'8010M or 2% of global turnover for essential entities; \'807M or 1.4% for important entities.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	5.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 24/72-hour incident reporting: 
\f1\b0 Strict notification deadlines to national Computer Security Incident Response Teams (CSIRTs).\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	6.	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 
\f0\b\fs22 Implementation timeframe: 
\f1\b0 Realistic compliance requires 6-12 months for most organizations.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb240\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs26 \cf3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Strategic Opportunity\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa180\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs22 \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Organizations that approach NIS2 strategically can achieve dual compliance objectives. Approximately 55% of NIS2 requirements overlap with GDPR obligations, and 75% align with ISO 27001 controls. A unified compliance program reduces overall effort while strengthening security posture and demonstrating regulatory diligence.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
