\f1\fs22 Harmonizing cybersecurity requirements across member states\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 {\listtext	\'95	} \'95	
\f1\fs22 Expanding scope to cover more sectors and entity sizes\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 {\listtext	\'95	} \'95	
\f1\fs22 Establishing minimum security measures for network and information systems\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 {\listtext	\'95	} \'95	
\f1\fs22 Strengthening cooperation between member states\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	} \'95	
\f1\fs22 Improving incident reporting and information sharing\
